Dash cast
    Events
        Unit - A unit Starts the effect of an ability
    Conditions
        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
            Conditions
                (Ability being cast) Equal to Swordsaint: Dash 
                (Ability being cast) Equal to Hellforged: Charge (Hellion Dash)
    Actions
        Set VariableSet Dash_MUI1 = (Dash_MUI1 + 1)
        -------- Dynamic indexing --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                Dash_MUI1 Greater than Dash_maxindex
            Then - Actions
                Set VariableSet Dash_MUI2[Dash_MUI1] = Dash_MUI1
                Set VariableSet Dash_maxindex = Dash_MUI1
            Else - Actions
        -------- ai is for "anti-inconvenicence" (integer) --------
        Set VariableSet Dash_ai = Dash_MUI2[Dash_MUI1]
        -------- Cast Setup --------
        Set VariableSet Dash_caster[Dash_ai] = (Triggering unit)
        Custom script:   set udg_Dash_dmg[udg_Dash_ai] = GetAbilityReal("herodur", udg_Dash_caster[udg_Dash_ai], getlvl(), GetSpellAbilityId())
        Custom script:   set udg_Dash_AoE[udg_Dash_ai] = GetAbilityReal("aoe", udg_Dash_caster[udg_Dash_ai], getlvl(), GetSpellAbilityId())
        Set VariableSet Dash_endpoint[Dash_ai] = (Target point of ability being cast)
        Set VariableSet Dash_alreadyDamaged[Dash_ai] = (Units within 0.00 of Dash_endpoint[Dash_ai].)
        -------- Visual setup --------
        Special Effect - Create a special effect attached to the origin of Dash_caster[Dash_ai] using Valiant Charge.mdx
        Set VariableSet Dash_attach[Dash_ai] = (Last created special effect)
        Animation - Play Dash_caster[Dash_ai]'s Spell Throw animation
        Unit - Pause Dash_caster[Dash_ai]
        Unit - Turn collision for Dash_caster[Dash_ai] Off.
        -------- begin looping --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (Dash loop <gen> is on) Equal to False
            Then - Actions
                Trigger - Turn on Dash loop <gen>
            Else - Actions
